ENSURE YOU HAVE THESE ON YOUR PRODJECT

1- A LABEL COLOUR CAN BE ANYTHING BUT MAGENTA
2- THE BACKGROUND COLOUR HAS TO BE MAGENTA 
3- SET BORDERSTYLE TO NONE
4- START POSITION NEEDS TO BE CENTERSCREEN
5- TRANSPARENCYKEY - MAGENTA

full tutorial at https://youtube.com/@v7d9

There is much more you can add to this like moving text ect but this is a basic template for beginners looking to up there game
to the next level 
